OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry, warm and sunny start to
OL,6,Fthe day. Turning even hotter as the
OL,7,Fday goes on with extreme heat
OL,8,Fcontinuing along with high humidity.
OL,9,FPerhaps some high cloud moving in at
OL,10,Ftimes in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying very warm and humid
OL,13,Fovernight. Elevated thunderstorms
OL,14,Fspreading northwards, turning very
OL,15,Fgusty with the odd rumble of thunder
OL,16,Fand possible hail. Low cloud moving
OL,17,Finto Cornwall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
