OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAlthough temperatures falling,
OL,6,Fstaying very warm with humidity levels
OL,7,Fremaining high. Cloud across Cornwall
OL,8,Flifts through the morning, leaving
OL,9,Fplenty of strong sunshine for all.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Fhot into the weekend, but temperatures
OL,13,Fslowly coming down by Sunday. Dry for
OL,14,Fmany but turning cloudier into the new
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
